<h2>Confirm your account as a lower tier waste carrier/broker/dealer</h2>

<p>To <%= @email %>,</p>

<p>Please select the link below to confirm your account and complete your registration as a lower tier waste carrier/broker/dealer.</p>
 
<p><%= link_to 'Confirm your account', confirmation_url(@resource, :confirmation_token => @token) %></p>

<p>The link above is valid for six hours. You can request this e-mail to be sent again with a new link from here: 
<%= link_to "Send new instructions to confirm my account", new_confirmation_url(:user) %>
<br/>
<p>Please contact the Environment Agency helpline on 03708 506506 if you have any questions about this.</p>
